<h3>Standards</h3>
<p>Section 508 = WCAG 2?</p>
<h4>Section 508</h4>
<p>First federal law</p>
<p>Could be monitored</p>
<p>Applied to State Govts</p>
<p>Applied to businesses</p>
<h4>WCAG 2.0</h4>
<p>Stable, referenceable technical standard</p>
<p>12 guidelines; 4 principles</p>
<p>Perceivable, Operable, Understandable, Robust</p>
<p>Testable success criteria, Three levels: A, AA, and AAA</p>
<p>webaim.org/resources/designers</p>
img/shuttle.jpg
