<p>Example: Making a "separate, accessible" website</p>
<h4>People</h4>
<p>What if they don't know?</p>
<p>Example: A developer doesn't use real buttons</p>
<h4>Details</h4>
<p>Hi, my name is minutia</p>
<p>Example: Ensuring your colors are high contrast</p>
